# Not required for Phase 0/1 — pytest.ini already defaults to the public
# ParaBank demo. To override, pass --base-url explicitly, e.g.:
#   pytest --base-url=http://localhost:8080/parabank/
# Trailing slash matters — see DEC-008 in docs/decision-log.md. Without it,
# a relative goto() path resets to the domain root instead of appending.
